" tridactylrc - vim-like keyboard navigation for Firefox
" 適用: Tridactyl の :source または起動時オートロード（native messenger 必須）

" === reset ===
sanitise tridactyllocal tridactylsync
unbindall

" === scroll ===
bind j scrollline 5
bind k scrollline -5
bind h scrollline -10 horizontal
bind l scrollline 10 horizontal
bind gg scrollto 0
bind G scrollto 100
bind d scrollpage 0.5
bind u scrollpage -0.5
bind <C-d> scrollpage 0.5
bind <C-u> scrollpage -0.5

" === tab ===
bind J tabprev
bind K tabnext
bind gT tabprev
bind gt tabnext
bind t fillcmdline tabopen
bind T fillcmdline tabopen -b
bind x tabclose
bind X undo
bind <A-1> tab 1
bind <A-2> tab 2
bind <A-3> tab 3
bind <A-4> tab 4
bind <A-5> tab 5
bind <A-6> tab 6
bind <A-7> tab 7
bind <A-8> tab 8
bind <A-9> tab 9

" === navigation ===
bind H back
bind L forward
bind r reload
bind R reloadhard
bind gh home

" === find ===
bind / fillcmdline find
bind ? fillcmdline find -?
bind n findnext 1
bind N findnext -1
bind <Esc> nohlsearch

" === hint ===
bind f hint
bind F hint -b
bind ;y hint -y
bind ;e hint -e
bind ;i hint -i
bind ;I hint -I
bind ;k hint -k
bind ;s hint -s
bind ;S hint -S
bind ;a hint -a
bind ;A hint -A

" === command bar ===
bind : fillcmdline_notrail
bind o fillcmdline open
bind O current_url open
bind w fillcmdline winopen
bind W current_url winopen

" === url manipulation ===
bind yy clipboard yank
bind p clipboard open
bind P clipboard tabopen

" === zoom ===
bind + zoom 0.1 true
bind - zoom -0.1 true
bind = zoom 1 false

" === source view ===
bind gf viewsource

" === settings ===
set hintchars asdfghjkl
set hintfiltermode vimperator-reflow
set tabopenpos last
set newtabfocus page
set smoothscroll true
set update.lastchecktime 0

" === blacklist - Tridactyl を一時無効化するサイト ===
" GitHub などキーバインドが豊富なサイトは衝突回避で除外可能
" blacklistadd mail.google.com
" blacklistadd github.com
